Distribution. This species was previously recorded for Saudi Arabia by
Abu-Zoherah et al . (1993)
. It was described from Sudan and is further recorded from the following areas: Palaearctic Region; Afghanistan , Algeria , Canary Islands, China , Egypt , Greece , Iran , Israel , Italy , Kenya , Korea , southern Norway , Mongolia , Morocco , Russia , Syria , Sweden , Tunisia , Turkey ; Afrotropical Region: Eritrea , Ethiopia , Kenya , Saudi Arabia and Yemen ( Smith & Vockeroth 1980 ; Peck 1988 ; Whittington 2003 ;
Birtele et al . 2010
;
Khosravian et al . 2015
;
Smit et al . 2017
;
Haffaressas et al . 2017
; Speight 2020 ;
Mebarkia et al . 2020
); Oriental Region: China , India , Pakistan ( Ghorpadé 2014 ;
Turk et al . 2015b
).
